{"content": "I need to multiply 800\u2089 \u00d7 335\u2089.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n800\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 0\u00d79\u00b9 + 0\u00d79\u2070 = 8\u00d781 + 0 + 0 = 648\u2081\u2080\n\n335\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 3\u00d79\u00b9 + 5\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 3\u00d79 + 5\u00d71 = 243 + 27 + 5 = 275\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n648 \u00d7 275 = 178,200\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n178200 \u00f7 9 = 19800 r 0\n19800 \u00f7 9 = 2200 r 0\n2200 \u00f7 9 = 244 r 4\n244 \u00f7 9 = 27 r 1\n27 \u00f7 9 = 3 r 0\n3 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 3\n\nReading from bottom to top: 301400\u2089\n\n**301400**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1150, "completion_tokens": 310}